# Skill Routing

## gstack (general)
When asked to review code, find bugs, or audit security — use gstack skills from ~/.claude/skills/gstack/:
- /review → Staff Engineer code review
- /qa-only → QA report only, no changes  
- /investigate → Root cause debugging
- /cso → Security audit (OWASP + STRIDE)
- /plan-eng-review → Architecture review

## FENCH QA Skill (project-specific)
When asked to audit Finch, check production readiness, review performance, or do a UX audit:
Load .agent/skills/finch-qa-auditor/SKILL.md and follow its instructions exactly.

Always read AGENTS.md and .planning/STATE.md before any audit task.